  <md:abstract><para>By the end of this section, you will be able to:</para><list>
<item>Describe the function and components of a heat engine</item>
<item>Explain the efficiency of an engine</item>
<item>Calculate the efficiency of an engine for a given cycle of an ideal gas</item></list></md:abstract>
